{
  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card, 9:16 ratio, in a vibrant and energetic illustrated comic book pop art style. The design features a dynamic split panel. On the left, a stylized cartoon character resembling a young person, with wide, anxious eyes and slightly furrowed brow, is depicted in a desaturated, sketched style. This character wears a black button-down shirt and has hands raised in a gesture of mild confusion or overwhelmedness. Above this character are two books, one red labeled \"Math\" and one green labeled \"Science,\" also in a slightly faded, sketched style. The text \"LEVEL 1 SUHAAN\" is displayed in bold, pixelated, white capital letters above the left panel. The background on the left is a dark blue, with faint, stylized circuit board patterns in neon blue and pink. On the right side of the split panel, the same stylized cartoon character is depicted with a bright, confident smile, transformed into a \"hero\" version. This character glows with a subtle golden aura and holds a golden trophy with both hands. Above this character, the text \"GRADE-UP! KNOWLEDGE UNLOCKED! CONFERENCE QUEST COMPLETE!\" is displayed in bold, pixelated, yellow capital letters with a slight glow. The background on the right is also dark blue with similar neon circuit board patterns, but they appear more vibrant and energetic, with brighter pinks and oranges. The word \"congratulations\" is prominently displayed across the bottom of the card in large, bold, white pixelated text with a glowing cyan and magenta outline, evoking a retro video game aesthetic. The overall mood is one of transformation and achievement, captured in a playful, exaggerated comic book style with a distinct GenZ visual language.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a greeting card, 9:16 ratio, in a vibrant and energetic illustrated comic book pop art style. The design is a subtle continuation of the front cover's theme, focusing on minimalist, abstract geometric patterns. The background is a deep, dark blue, transitioning into streaks of neon pink, purple, and electric blue, reminiscent of digital data streams or light trails. These patterns are rendered with a clean, stylized linework, suggesting technological advancement. In the center-left area, subtle, stylized representations of achievement motifs like faint golden starbursts or small trophy outlines are integrated into the pattern, hinting at the character's success without being explicit. There is no text. The bottom-right corner, approximately a 1-inch square area, is completely clear and undecorated to reserve space for a QR code. The overall mood is serene yet technologically infused, providing a quiet, artistic conclusion to the celebratory narrative.",
  "leftInterior": "Left interior spread of a greeting card, 9:16 ratio, in a vibrant and energetic illustrated comic book pop art style. This panel continues the narrative from the front cover, showcasing the \"before\" state. A stylized cartoon character, mirroring the one on the front cover, is depicted with a look of mild distress and confusion, hands spread wide. This character is surrounded by an abundance of stylized, open textbooks in muted colors. The text \"Last Year.\" is clearly written in a clean, sans-serif font above this figure. The background is a deep, muted blue with faint, less vibrant circuit board patterns and scattered digital static effects. The overall aesthetic emphasizes the academic challenge and effort that preceded the success, rendered in a slightly desaturated and sketch-like manner to contrast with the later depiction of achievement.",
  "rightInterior": "Right interior spread of a greeting card, 9:16 ratio, in a vibrant and energetic illustrated comic book pop art style. This panel is the climax of the visual story, showcasing the \"after\" state and featuring the main message. The same stylized cartoon character, now radiant and confident, holds a gleaming golden trophy. The character is enveloped in a warm, golden aura, signifying \"main character energy.\" Surrounding the character are stylized, explosive graphic elements like \"KAPOW!\" (for grades), \"ZAP!\" (for up-leveling), and \"BOOM!\" (for conferences), rendered in bold, comic-style lettering. The background is a dynamic mix of bright, celebratory sunbeam patterns and vibrant neon circuit board lines in electric blues, pinks, and oranges, creating a sense of energetic triumph. The main message, \"Suhaan, NO CAP, you absolutely obliterated this year. It's giving main character energy with the god-tier grades and leveling up in every single subject. You even went conference hunting?! The academic glow-up is real, periodt. Slay! - Neelu,\" is presented in a beautiful, clearly readable handwritten cursive script. The handwriting has a natural, flowing character with slight variations in line weight, appearing as if written with an elegant pen. This script is integrated seamlessly into the artwork, perhaps flowing across the triumphant scene or nestled within a stylized, abstract digital frame. The overall mood is exuberant and celebratory, perfectly capturing the GenZ humor and unhinged vibes through its bold visuals and energetic presentation."
